I ordered 2 pizzas, wings, and a 2 liter soda from here on Ubereats and I am disappointed. I only received 1 pizza, even though I ordered 2. The delivery guy came on a bike and he claimed that this store only gave him 1 pizza. Then I called this store and they said they gave the delivery guy my whole order. I'm extremely upset right now. What a waste of $43 (including tip), and I had to go downstairs, even though I specifically asked for the delivery man to come upstairs in my instructions. Only reason I rated 2 stars is because the delivery guy showed some sort of remorse and Ubereats Customer Service will refund me for the missing pizza, after o filed a complaint. Very disappointed, never ordering from here again
